---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer" description="Legal disclaimer, affiliate disclosure, and risk warning for Passive Yield Lab.">
  <div class="page-content">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>

    <h2>Not Financial Advice</h2>
    <p>
      The content on Passive Yield Lab is for educational and informational purposes only.
      Nothing published on this website constitutes financial, investment, tax,
      or legal advice. You should always do your own research and consult a
      qualified financial advisor before making any investment decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>Risk Warning</h2>
    <p>
      Cryptocurrency investments carry a high degree of risk. The value of
      digital assets can go to zero. DeFi protocols, staking mechanisms, and
      exchange-based products may contain bugs, suffer from exploits, or become
      insolvent. You could lose some or all of your invested capital. Past
      yields and returns are not indicative of future performance.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Passive Yield Lab participates in affiliate programs with various cryptocurrency
      exchanges, hardware wallet manufacturers, and software providers. When you
      click on certain links and sign up for a product or service, we may
      receive a referral commission at no additional cost to you.
    </p>
    <p>
      Affiliate relationships never influence our editorial content. We only
      recommend products and services that we have personally used and believe
      provide genuine value. However, you should be aware that financial
      incentives exist.
    </p>
    <p>
      Articles that contain affiliate links are clearly marked with a
      disclosure banner at the top of the page.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      We strive to keep all information accurate and up to date, but the crypto
      space moves fast. APYs, product features, fee structures, and protocol
      mechanics can change at any time. Always verify current details directly
      with the platform before committing funds.
    </p>

    <h2>No Guarantees</h2>
    <p>
      Passive Yield Lab makes no representations or warranties regarding the accuracy,
      completeness, or timeliness of any content. Use this site at your own
      risk.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
